column1: #Text=Wikinews interviews Stephen Murphy about the upcoming by-election in the Higgins electorate of the Australian parliament
#Text=With two by-elections coming up in Australia , many minor parties and independents will be looking to gain a seat in the House of Representatives .
#Text=Stephen Murphy is one of the independents .
#Text=Mr Murphy is a computer programmer from the Melbourne suburb of Brunswick .
#Text=" After growing up in South-East Melbourne I studied Science at Monash with first class Honours , worked in Europe for 10 years and have recently returned to Australia .
